query:
SELECT 
  s.smshubCode,
  s.name as service,
  c.name as country,
  a.name as api,
  COUNT(*) as count
FROM prices p
JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
GROUP BY p.countryId, p.serviceId, p.apiId
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY count DESC, s.name;
